info.summary: 1x1 Park lots using the Street Planters and Benches prop set
info.description:
Four very simple lots using differently rotated street planter & bench props. Useful for gap filling in parks or among developed areas.
Placing these plazas provides residential cap relief to the value of 1,000 per lot per R-wealth category and raises commercial and residential desirability in the immediate vicinity.
info.author: mattb325
